<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rì zi yī tiān tiān de guò qù 迦南365</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rì zi yī tiān yī tiān de guò qù, yòu yào yíng lái yī gè míng tiān,
 jīn tiān nǐ suǒ zuò de zǐ xì jiǎn diǎn, shì fǒu dōu méng shén jì niàn,
 shèng jīng nǐ kàn méi kàn, dǎo gào yǒu duō shǎo biàn,
 zuò le duō shǎo shàn shì, nǐ xīn lǐ yǒu méi yǒu kuī qiàn,
 zǒu qiān lǐ zǒu wàn lǐ yuǎn, jī dū tú de shēng huó yào jìng qián,
 yī chén bù rǎn, méi yǒu wū diǎn, zhè yàng shén cái zhēn xǐ huān.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>365</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>